Ta có: 
		{\begin{align*}
				&2x^4-3x^2=-x^2+2\Leftrightarrow 2x^4-2x^2-2=0\\
				\Leftrightarrow&\left[\begin{aligned}& x^2=\dfrac{1-\sqrt{5}}{2}\quad \text{(loại)} \\
					& x^2=\dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2} 
				\end{aligned}\right.\Leftrightarrow x=\pm \sqrt{\dfrac{1+\sqrt{5}}{2}.}
	\end{align*}
